Simplifies the creation of large, grid-based 2D worlds.
Integrates seamlessly with game engines such as Unity and Godot.
Supports advanced features like auto-tiling, layers, and multiple worlds.
Optimized for fast iteration and prototyping.
Offers an intuitive UI for designers and a JSON export format for programmers.
Developed by Sébastien Bénard, the lead developer of Dead Cells.

Website: https://ldtk.io
